OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChildren's futures at risk 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas more put to work - ILO  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The future of millions of children is  
OL,6, at risk as growing numbers are pulled  
OL,7, out of school and into work, the head  
OL,8, of the United Nations' labour body has 
OL,9, told the BBC.                          
OL,11,FGilbert Houngbo, director-general of   
OL,12,Fthe International Labour Organization  
OL,13,F(ILO), said there had been a           
OL,14,F"regression" in regions around the     
OL,15,Fworld amid global economic problems.   
OL,17,FSome of the worst forms of work        
OL,18,Finvolved sexual exploitation.          
OL,20,FHe said urgent action was needed.      
